OL,3,CHome Bargains pledges 'remarkable'
OL,4,C#2.5m to Zoe's Place campaign
OL,6,FITV Granada's Victoria Grimes spoke to
OL,7,Fa fundraiser from Zoe's Place after
OL,8,Fthe huge pledge was made
OL,10,FHigh-street retailer Home Bargains has
OL,11,Fpledged a "remarkable" #2.5 million to
OL,12,Fa campaign to save a specialist baby
OL,13,Fhospice at risk of closure.
OL,15,FZoe's Place has provided palliative
OL,16,Fand end-of-life care for children up
OL,17,Fto five-years-old but is now facing
OL,18,Fclosure after failing to find funding
OL,19,Ffor a new building before its lease
OL,20,Fruns out at the end of the year.
