OL,3,CHome Bargains pledges 'remarkable'
OL,4,C#2.5m to Zoe's Place campaign
OL,6,FOn Monday, 28 October, Liverpool-based
OL,7,Fretailer TJ Morris Ltd made a
OL,8,F"remarkable" pledge of #2.5 million,
OL,9,Fwhich the charity says will provide
OL,10,F"crucial hope for the children and
OL,11,Ffamilies" who are supported by Zoe's
OL,12,FPlace.
OL,14,FThe charity, based in West Derby in
OL,15,FLiverpool, has now raised half of the
OL,16,F#6.4 million they needed to help build
OL,17,Fa new facility and keep the hospice in
OL,18,Fthe city.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
