OL,4,C#2.5m to Zoe's Place campaign
OL,6,FJoan Stainsby, Executive Trustee of
OL,7,FZoe's Place, added: "This
OL,8,Funprecedented pledge reflects the
OL,9,Fgenerosity and overwhelming support we
OL,10,Fare experiencing from the Liverpool
OL,11,Fcommunity and beyond.
OL,13,F"As a charity, we are immensely
OL,14,Fgrateful to Home Bargains for standing
OL,15,Fby us in our time of need."
