OL,3,CHome Bargains pledges 'remarkable'
OL,4,C#2.5m to Zoe's Place campaign
OL,6,FHome Bargains previously committed to
OL,7,Ffund vital elements of the new
OL,8,Fhospice, including an on-site
OL,9,Fhydrotherapy pool designed to provide
OL,10,Fcomfort and relief to children with
OL,11,Fvarious health conditions.
OL,13,FThe charity says their latest pledge
OL,14,Fis a "pivotal moment" for the
OL,15,Fhospice's future.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, John Bishop and Jason
OL,18,FManford are among a long line-up of
OL,19,Fcomedians have taken to the mic for a
OL,20,Fcomedy show fundraiser in aid of Zoe's
OL,21,FPlace.
